    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you need to print the number you can use printf</p>\n\n<pre><code>System.out.printf(\"%02d\", num);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>You can use</p>\n\n<pre><code>String.format(\"%02d\", num);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>(num &lt; 10 ? \"0\" : \"\") + num;\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or</p>\n\n<pre><code>(\"\"+(100+num)).substring(1);\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
